text: Area code 767 is a telephone area code in the North American Numbering Plan. It covers the Commonwealth of Dominica, an island nation in the Caribbean Sea. Area code 767 was established in 1997 to serve Dominica's telecommunications needs. The number 767 stands for the letters ROS and may be mnemonic for Roseau, Dominica's capital city.
